  "name": "Release Notes v3.15.1 - POS and Back Office",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"release-notes-v3-15-1-pos-and-back-office\">Release Notes v3.15.1 - POS and Back Office</h1>\n<p>In this release we've made a small number of improvements and resolutions to Retail Express.</p>\n<div>\n<p>This update will be made available to all customers between <strong>7th February</strong> - <strong>15th February</strong>.</p>\n</div><br/><br/><hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"improvements\">Improvements</h2>\n<h3 data-id=\"special-orders-report\">Special Orders Report</h3>\n<p>We've added some additional features to the Special Orders Report. </p>\n<ul><li>The customer's Email address is now displayed in the Results tab<br/><img alt=\"mceclip1 - 2023-07-09T185938.959.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcgEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Added Order Source and Sales Channels (Web Stores) to the Filter options<br/><img alt=\"mceclip0 - 2023-07-09T185943.471.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfcqEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li></ul><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<h3 data-id=\"help-support-menu\">Help &amp; Support Menu</h3>\n<p>We've updated the Back Office \"Help &amp; Support\" menu to make it more useful!</p>\n<p><img alt=\"mceclip0 - 2023-07-09T185948.800.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000ppfO6EAI.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<p>With the new menu update, you can now access important information faster than ever, including:</p>\n<ul><li>Product Portal (to view our development roadmap, and provide feedback on ideas)</li><li>Announcements (stay up-to-date with the latest news and Release Notes)</li><li>Training Academy</li><li>Contact Support (although you can also reach support directly from the <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Announcing-the-Knowledge-Base-in-Back-Office\">\"Help\" button</a> now available in the Back Office)</li></ul><p>Please note we've also renamed several options:</p>\n<ul><li>\"Implementation\" has been renamed to \"Onboarding Console\"</li><li>\"My Retail Express Invoices and Payments\" has been renamed to \"My Account\"</li></ul><p>Access the new menu by clicking the Help &amp; Support menu in Back Office.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#top\">Back to top</a></p>\n<hr></hr><h2 data-id=\"resolutions\">Resolutions</h2>\n<ul><li>The Franchise Connect Sync History report can now be run successfully without timeout errors</li></ul>",
